        <description>
            <geninfo>
                <para>MaxxForce DT engines are experiencing inadvertent low coolant warning light/buzzer activation.
                </para>
                <para>It has been determined by International Truck and Engine Corporation that the above listed models
                    were built with an EGR cooler deaeration hose that the inside diameter is too large and the
                    restrictor fitting needs to be installed.
                </para>
            </geninfo>
        </description>
